## Data Flow: Complete AI Pipeline

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant CLI as Tripartite1 CLI
    participant P as Pathos Agent
    participant L as Logos Agent
    participant E as Ethos Agent
    participant CE as Consensus Engine
    participant Mur as Murmur (Memory)
    participant CR as CascadeRouter
    participant PFA as Privacy-First-Analytics
    participant Cloud as Cloud LLM (optional)

    User->>CLI: Submit Query
    CLI->>PFA: Track Query Start

    CLI->>P: Process Intent
    P->>Mur: Recall Context
    Mur-->>P: Relevant Memories
    P-->>CLI: Intent Analysis

    CLI->>L: Process Logic
    L->>Mur: Recall Knowledge
    Mur-->>L: Relevant Facts
    L-->>CLI: Solution Plan

    CLI->>E: Verify Safety
    E->>CR: Check Hardware Capability
    CR-->>E: Capability Report
    E-->>CLI: Safety Verification

    CLI->>CE: Aggregate Agent Outputs
    CE->>CE: Calculate Consensus

    alt Consensus Achieved
        CE-->>CLI: Consensus Result
        CLI->>Mur: Store Interaction
        CLI->>PFA: Track Success
        CLI-->>User: Response
    else Consensus Not Achieved
        CE->>CLI: Revision Round
        CLI->>CR: Escalate to Cloud?
        CR->>Cloud: Route to Stronger Model
        Cloud-->>CR: Enhanced Response
        CR-->>CLI: Cloud Result
        CLI->>PFA: Track Escalation
        CLI-->>User: Enhanced Response
    end

    CLI->>PFA: Track Query Complete
```

